- "highest score" refers to the participant with the maximum total score;
- "first event" refers to the event with ID 1.

- "performers" refers to participants;
- "guardians" refers to judges;
- "land of challenges" refers to the nationality of the participants and judges;
- "arena" refers to the event;
- "first event" refers to the event with `event_id` 1.

- "In the grand arena of competition" refers to a competitive event or tournament;
